@startuml
title API Service Responsibility Boundary

' ===============================
' Shared Style
' ===============================
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Inter
skinparam defaultFontSize 14
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center

top to bottom direction

skinparam rectangle {
  RoundCorner 8
  BorderColor #1F2937
  FontColor #111827
}

skinparam arrow {
  Color #374151
  Thickness 1.5
}

skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #F9FAFB
  BorderColor #9CA3AF
  FontColor #374151
}

' ===============================
' Responsibility Domains
' ===============================

rectangle #DBEAFE "API Service\n\n\
- Authentication & authorization\n\
- Schema & structural validation\n\
- Semantic business validation\n\
- Deterministic derivations\n\
- Referential integrity checks\n\
- Durable fact persistence" as API

rectangle #DCFCE7 "Persistence Boundary\n\n\
- Durable facts recorded\n\
- Database guarantees applied\n\
- Change becomes observable" as PB

rectangle #FEE2E2 "Outside API Responsibility\n\n\
- Business meaning & interpretation\n\
- Business-driven enrichment\n\
- Domain workflows & policies\n\
- Side effects & notifications\n\
- Integrations & projections" as OUT

API --> PB : Persist to Database
PB --> OUT : Event Stream

note right of PB
Persistence is the execution boundary.
API responsibility ends here.
end note

@enduml
